CS414_P1
Party A
User stories
09/20/2019
1. As a user, I want to register to this X game platform by using an email,
nickname and a password in order to login it and play it online.
2. As a user, I want to invite anther user who is online
3. As a user, the user who is be invited can accept or ignore.
4. As a user, I can receive a notification from the user if he reject it.
5. (optional) As a user, I want to send more than one invitation.
6. (optional) As a user, I want to play multiple games at the same time.
7. As a user, I want this platform to record the history of the game including the result of
the game, the player account of the opponent, and the number of moves.
8. As a user, I want to have a prompt to tell me what is my turn.
9. As a user, I want to have rules and tutorials before I start playing the game for the first
time.
10. As a user, I want to quit from any game at any time.
11. As a user, I want to logout this X game whenever I do not want to play, and the
platform prompts you before you exit.
12. As a user, I want to be able to unregister.
